<br>
<br>
Chain rooter (single target root and bonds of force - ae root)<br>
<br>
Chain stunner (this guy ROCKS!!!! Seriously he really rocks hardcore. Did I mention he rocks?!? Cause he does! Honest!)<br>
<br>
Balanced (casts 4 different style nukes plus stun and root)<br>
<br>
Melee (usual crappy version that never casts much)<br>
<br>
<br>
The chain stunning pet kicks ass. I was teamed up with my epic pet and another 60 mage with the 58 fire pet (chain stunner flavor)...I had others hits on, and one of our pets took a hit from mushrooms or shadel bandits, about every 10 seconds or so during combat. =)))))) I couldn't believe my eyes.<br>
<br>
Allow me to reiterate that. With a 58 chain stunning fire pet, and my epic pet, our pets took almost no damage EVER. I've never seen the word &quot;Stunned&quot; so much in my life. The damn little turd of a fire pet managed to mitigate almost all damage from the mobs we were fighting (again tested in FG).<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
 <p><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=27498">Wayfarer Jones</a>
